tickets.title: Need help with Math homework
tickets.body: I'm having trouble understanding the concepts of calculus, especially related to derivatives and integrals. Can someone provide me with additional resources or explanations? Thank you!

tickets.title: Request for career counseling
tickets.body: I'm a sophomore and I'm unsure about which major to choose. I would like to discuss career options and get advice on planning my future path. Any guidance would be appreciated.

tickets.title: Issue with registration process
tickets.body: I'm encountering an error message when trying to register for courses online. It says my student ID is invalid, but I have verified it with the administration. Can someone assist me in resolving this issue?

tickets.title: Question about campus parking
tickets.body: I'm a new student and I'm confused about the parking regulations on campus. Can someone clarify where students are allowed to park and if there are any permits required?

tickets.title: Technical issue with library database
tickets.body: I'm trying to access research articles for my assignment, but I'm encountering a technical error when using the library database. Is there someone who can help troubleshoot this issue?

tickets.title: Inquiry about study abroad programs
tickets.body: I'm interested in studying abroad next semester and would like more information about the application process, available programs, and financial aid options. Can someone provide guidance?

tickets.title: Problem with dormitory heating
tickets.body: The heating in my dorm room is not working properly, and it's becoming uncomfortable especially during the colder months. How can I request maintenance to fix this issue?

tickets.title: Request for accessibility accommodations
tickets.body: I require specific accommodations for accessibility purposes during exams and class activities. Whom should I contact to arrange these accommodations?

tickets.title: Query about student health services
tickets.body: I'm feeling unwell and would like to schedule an appointment with the student health services. How can I book an appointment and what services are available?

tickets.title: Concern about cafeteria food options
tickets.body: I have dietary restrictions and I'm concerned about the variety and quality of food options available in the cafeteria. Can someone provide information on special dietary accommodations?
